ATTRIBUTION AND MODIFICATIONS

Velacritty contains substantial portions of the Alacritty codebase, including:
  - Core terminal emulation engine
  - GPU-accelerated rendering system
  - Cross-platform compatibility layer
  - Configuration system
  - Vi mode implementation
  - Search functionality
  - And many other components

Modifications in Velacritty include:
  - Enhanced visual customization features
  - Improved scrolling behavior
  - Additional user experience enhancements
  - Project rebranding and documentation updates

